reviewText: Explains popular scams and how to avoid them, give you the Ten Commandments of Financial Security, explains how insurance (life, health, disability and property) can help and how to buy what is right for you.  Also explains Estate Planning, Wills, Revocable Living Trust and Probate.  I  recommend it.
The ten commandments of financial security is worth the price.  Views insurance products, what you can use them for, how to buy them cheap and how much to buy.  Great stuff!  I recommend.
